<emphasis id="B967615F2F73FFF84D95FA52FBEAF9AA" box="[1021,1077,1517,1542]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">et al.</emphasis>
(2010), Kohlsdorf 
<emphasis id="B967615F2F73FFF84B64FA52FA9BF9AA" box="[1292,1348,1517,1542]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="160">et al.</emphasis>
